==English==

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/tɑːsk/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# a [[piece]] of [[work]] done as [[part]] of one’s [[duty|duties]]
# a [[difficult]] or [[tedious]] [[undertaking]]
# an [[objective]]
# {{computing}} a [[process]] or [[execution]] of a program.

